race.comment: BEST COFFEE (2) finished third over 1400m at Sunshine Coast at his most recent appearance on December 14. Won his only start at this track and distance. One of the genuine hopes in the race. PUROSANGUE (1) was an impressive winner last time over 1200m at this track, leading throughout and putting 5.5 lengths on his rivals. Sure to run well again. JE REVE (5) finished third last start, beaten 1.75 lengths at Warwick over 1200m. Should give this a shake. STORM FORCE TEN (4) is looking to break through after filling a minor placing at both starts this campaign, last time out when third over 1300m at Rockhampton. In the mix.
